    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-08-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-08-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="1081"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1081">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        German Ambassador</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_BJHACV1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bernstorff</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1915</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Ambassador</hi>: I have received your note of
                    the 8th instant, in explanation of the action of the officers of a German
                    torpedo boat in holding up the American steamship <hi rend="italic"
                        >Muskogee</hi> and <pb facs="1010" n="752" xml:id="pg_752"/> the removal
                    from the vessel of two of its seamen, and beg to thank you for your attention to
                    the matter.</p>
                <p>You will appreciate that this Government cannot acquiesce in a practice which
                    might be regarded as lending assistance to deserting seamen from American
                    vessels on the high seas.</p>
                <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
